I"x<p>This project analyzes Reddit posts about the new Nintendo Switch 2 to perform sentiment analysis and categorize emotional tones as positive, negative, or neutral across various gaming subreddits. By mapping these sentiments to specific topics and identifying dominant emotions, we gain crucial insights into overall community sentiment and pinpoint areas of widespread concern or positive engagement. This direct understanding of public sentiment from Reddit is vital for understanding trends, informing content strategies, and identifying key discussion drivers.
